{"tid":2500151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長沙灣黑社會菜檔 影相比公仔佬恐嚇","createTime":"2021-04-22T11:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T12:33:35.000Z","uid":109428,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6b639e2cfbdb59097b1942feac874d8d00e8442b","tid":2500151,"uid":109428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:59:55.000Z","msg":"事源有個呀伯想影低間野搞到成地垃圾 然後比人恐嚇 同類型事件都唔係第一次 有街坊指佢地有睇場<br />\n呢個位本身係好出名嘅老鼠燒臘檔 大慶 <br />\n後來執左就變左呢間永昇行<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZzuiJtM4KTfeA27y4NyXG8bMb7BLTj9JBNaFaJMzxkBG?filename=kqTf2d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkqTf2d5.jpg&h=d68147a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdGhgyuxK2WkawsqhbrMpvyaUDNjhE99hLoRHeRxABU68?filename=oPJcj10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoPJcj10.jpg&h=ef5d048b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過年個陣仲霸埋條行車線嚟擺貨賣貨<br />\n我本人都報過警 1823咩都試過<br />\n食環嚟到話馬路唔關佢事 <br />\n狗嚟到就傾兩句了事<br />\n日日大嗌已經騷擾到附近居民 仲霸咁多位嚟擺佢d垃圾同貨<br />\n報狗同1823都冇用 議員跟進過都搞唔掂伯<br />\n仲可以點對付佢<br />\n<br />\n地址 青山道永隆街交界<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmY5Xmi94BAwiyHgnHzk463kp8wFKWxLMGLMMhUkEKKuJB?filename=5M4Sj2u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5M4Sj2u.png&h=2936328d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a006ed59347258a60b31b4ee041decc3d4ab31b3","tid":2500151,"uid":109428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:02:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"831134a8e9b47408f2d638e3562cc605ddfc280f","tid":2500151,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:02:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad62a43ad5cd93c35539c460727c100c9d69017d","tid":2500151,"uid":361751,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:04:33.000Z","msg":"721都未平反<br />\n<br />\n你呢啲小事